# Development Phases

The project follows a phased approach:

## Phase 1: MVP - Core Simulation Loop
- Basic end-to-end implementation with minimal features
- Simple Python scripts with basic state management
- CLI or simple HTML interface
- Core LLM, RunwayML, and ElevenLabs API integration
- 5-turn simulation loop
- See [build-plan.md](mdc:build-plan.md) for details (Lines 10-95)

## Phase 2: Agents & State Management
- Google Agent Development Kit (GADK) implementation
- Redis for persistent state management
- Proper async handling of API calls
- CreativeDirectorAgent, VideoAgent, NarrationAgent

## Phase 3: Critique Loops & Error Handling
- Self-critique capabilities for content generation
- Robust error handling and retry logic
- Configuration management

## Phase 4: Production Front-End & Deployment
- Vercel web UI (React/Vue)
- Cloudflare R2 for media storage
- Full deployment

## Phase 5: Testing & Hardening
- End-to-end testing
- Monitoring, logging, cost controls
- User feedback incorporation
